text: Nils Andersson (24 October 1889 - 2 September 1973) was a Swedish swimmer. He competed in two events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1889 births Category:1973 deaths Category:Swedish male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Sweden Category:Swimmers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm Category:Male breaststroke swimmers
